## 📘 06 - Forms

This section explains how to create forms in HTML.  
Forms are used to collect user input.

---

## 📂 Files Included

1. 01-basic-form.html  
   → Basic `<form>` structure

2. 02-input-types.html  
   → Important input types

3. 03-radio-checkbox.html  
   → Radio buttons and checkboxes

4. 04-select-option.html  
   → Dropdown using `<select>` and `<option>`

5. 05-textarea-button.html  
   → `<textarea>` and `<button>`

6. 06-advanced-form-elements.html  
   → Advanced form features

